	   <tr><td colspan=2>The cheapest horse is around 8k (with cha buffed). The really nice thing is that 8k gets you 90% of what is useful about a horse. The speed aspect is mostly a red-herring (get yourself 10 sow potions for 1k, and those should last you quite a while). The real benefit for casters is that you are effectively always sitting, but with no agro! I've heard horses described as FT 10 for this very reason!<br><br>A horse is going to be my next purchace... then some rubies :-)<br><br>&nbsp;<br>You gain experience!<br>The Goblin Warlord hits YOU for 50 points!<br></td></tr>
