	   <tr><td colspan=2>There is one way I know of that raises faction with the bashers. When you first come into grobb before you cross the stream look in the cove on the right side. One of the bashers there is looking for fire beetle eyes (not sure how many he wants but think it is 4). This is the only quest besides the froglok tadpole flesh and froglok meat that you can turn into the warrior guild leader, but you need pretty decent faction to be able to do this one. Hope this helps some.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
